#This folder contains a crash course on C++ for CFD engineers. The idea is that the problems here are somewhat generic and you have 
a lot of freedom in the choice of implementation. 


#All modules should compile with the following lines:

cd <ModuleName>
mkdir build
cmake ..
make


#Module description:
-Module_0_intro 
 An introduction to classes and the CMake compilation framework. 

-Module_1_memory
 Memory management/containers/IO. 

-Module_2_mathlibrary
 Operator overloading, Libraries and unittesting

-Module_3_mpi
 MPI communication <This is not done yet!>

